'''ᱮᱸᱰᱩᱨᱤ ᱯᱤᱴᱷᱟ.''' ᱫᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ [[ᱳᱰᱤᱭᱟ]] ᱚᱲᱟᱜ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱡᱚᱢᱟᱜ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾ <ref name="DUBEY2010">{{cite book|author=KRISHNA GOPAL DUBEY|title=THE INDIAN CUISINE|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=_xiwkbgJbSQC&pg=PA151|date=27 September 2010|publisher=PHI Learning Pvt. Ltd.|isbn=978-81-203-4170-8|pages=151–}}</ref> ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱫᱟ [[ᱪᱟᱣᱞᱮ]] ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱦᱚᱞᱚᱝ ᱟᱨ [[ᱵᱤᱨᱤ]] ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱦᱚᱞᱚᱝ ᱠᱟ ᱞᱮᱣᱦᱟᱭ ᱛᱮ, ᱡᱟᱦᱟᱱᱟᱜ ᱪᱚᱸᱫᱟ ᱡᱤᱱᱤᱥ ᱨᱮ ᱫᱚᱦᱚ ᱠᱟᱛᱮ, ᱪᱩᱞᱦᱟ. ᱥᱮᱝᱜᱮᱞ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱚ ᱵᱷᱟᱸᱯ ᱤᱥᱤᱱᱟ ᱾ ᱠᱷᱟᱥ ᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱫᱚ [[ᱯᱨᱚᱛᱷᱚᱢᱟᱥᱴᱚᱢᱤ]] ᱨᱮ [[ᱳᱰᱤᱭᱟ]] ᱚᱲᱟᱜ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱚ ᱛᱮᱭᱟᱨᱻᱟ ᱾ <ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-otherstates/oriyas-prefer-enduri-pitha-on-prathamashtami/article923205.ece |title=The Hindu: Oriyas prefer ‘Enduri Pitha' on ‘Prathamashtami' |first= |last= |work=thehindu.com|quote=‘Enduri Pitha' a traditional delicacy of Orissa to showcase the medicinal properties of turmeric plant was prepared in most Oriya households on Monday to mark the celebration of ‘Prathamashtami' |accessdate=3 December 2012}}</ref>
